.SYNOPSIS
    Active Directory change review script with Tier-0 reporting, zero-change reporting, combined overview, and CSV exports. Comments have been added throughout to explain the purpose of each major section and function.

.DESCRIPTION
    Queries domain controller security logs for the same event IDs used by the original script, summarizes adds/removes/changes, exports CSV reports, and provides an interactive menu.
